title: All Los Angeles County beaches placed under high bacteria warning due to rain
dc:creator: Jonah Valdez
description: Public health officials warn people to avoid contact with water at all of L.A. County's beaches after rainfall pushed high levels of bacteria into the ocean.
content:encoded: Public health officials warn people to avoid contact with water at all of L.A. County's beaches after rainfall pushed high levels of bacteria into the ocean.
